  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5530751">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5530751/" class="title-link">陈寅恪诗抄</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5530751"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1787063/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1787063-9.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1787063/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">酒药女佛</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-08-02"
      class="main-meta">2012-08-02 16:41:19</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5530751_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  徐梵澄说过，陈寅恪的诗和乃父陈三立，乃兄陈师曾不能比，少有清词丽句。他晚年的作品似乎怨气太重，又晦涩，余英时和胡文辉的解释，还有很多牵强之处。一味钻那牛犄角，意义也不大。我倒最喜欢他抗战前後的作品，用典遣词都大气，大致可以熟读成诵。昨晚重翻一遍，摘抄在这里...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5530751/#comments">(4回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">7有用 / 2没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5530751_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5530751_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



